{"tid":20676,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【梁天琦認懦弱　怕即時還柙而沒有站在最前線反釋法】","createTime":"2016-12-03T13:16:12.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T13:16:12.000Z","uid":12721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e5397d6976f3c0409beefd5149a200a2f89b3427","tid":20676,"uid":12721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T13:16:12.000Z","msg":"本土民主前線發言人梁天琦接受now新聞專訪，被問到為何之前一直沒有回應宣誓風波和中國釋法事件，他說，若要反釋法自己便要鼓吹更多人出來，但自己卻無法站在最前線，因不想變成「叫人去做自己唔做」，所以選擇沉默，並坦承自己懦弱，不想現在便被即時還柙，就沒有站在最前線反釋法道歉。（節錄）<br />\n<br />\nSource：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/localpresshk/posts/1844158415800631\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flocalpresshk%2Fposts%2F1844158415800631&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXGwv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=a77914ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/localpresshk/posts/1844158415800631</a>"}]}